  <text>
    <body>
      <ab type="lido:objectWorkType">Photograph</ab>
      <ab subtype="creation" type="lido:event">
        <date>1939-1943</date>
      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The picture shows the interior of the ‘Rozafat’ cinema in Tirana in approximately 1940. The first floor is divided into four sectors. The first sector in the foreground is equipped with benches only. The second is equipped with chairs and separated by a bar from the third sector. This again is separated by a bar from the fourth sector, which is slightly elevated. The seats on the gallery are ascending.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The separation of seats into sectors suggests that the tickets were priced accordingly.</ab>
